reviewText: I bought this for my son.  He is thrilled to have all these fun movies in one package.  Arrived quickly.
Product not as described. Watch out.
great two movie combo pak. if you have not seen these movies then i recommend you do

Anchorman is honestly one of my all time favorites. Will Ferrell is amazing in this movie. The other two movies included in this buddle are just the icing on an already amazing cake. If you love Saturday Night Live you love the casts in these three films.
